messages.text: Okay. Well, take some Advil or something, rest, drink a lot of water.
Babe, I can’t help you if you don’t describe to me what’s going on.
Okay. Well, lie down. Take it easy.
Maybe go to sleep early tonight.
The thermometer is in the cabinet above the sink. Take your temperature and tell me what it is.
You need to get a cold rag and put it on your head.
Get a rag from the drawer and drench it in cold water.
If you’re feeling too bad, go get Mr. Webb across the street.
Calm down and try to take deep breaths.
Do you want me to call someone?
We can’t babe. Dad and I are five hours away, remember?
Do you know where you could’ve possibly gotten it?
This fever? Was there anyone at school who seemed sick?
no, not that i knew of
I’m sure you’ll be fine. Just get that cold rag and rest.
i feel like there is something caught in my throat
idk… bunch of phlegm or something
Do you feel like you need to throw-up?
Just stuff caught in your throat?
Try and get it out. See if that helps.
zach, maybe he gave me this
Then how could he have given you this?
he warned me something like this would happen
it was an innocent thing. we did it as a joke
zach, this boy in our class performed a ritual on us so he could curse us
cause we made fun of him at lunch
he was the outcast…sat by himself and we thought it would be fun to go sit by him
How is that making fun of him?
we would steal his stuff and say things to him, mean things
i didnt, i just sat at the table and watched the others do it
it was mostly gabby and tori
And you think he cursed you??
thats what he told us. yesterday when we tried to do it again
And this is why you’re sick??
ya he told us yesterday that he went home and cursed us
we didnt believe it either…said he set up ash circles and candles and such…
had each of our names and hair…not sure how he got it
we werent bullying him, we were just havin fun
it was all a good laugh…we didnt mean to hurt him
Well, sometimes babe, just sitting there and watching it happen is condoning it.
i wanted to tell them to stop
i would’ve if i would’ve known this would happen
Babe, curses aren’t real. He couldn’t have caused this.
It’s just a coincidence. You just have a bad fever and need rest.
he told us an ancient plague would befall us
He was just trying to scare you. And it worked.
Do you feel like you need to go to the hospital?
I’m sorry babe. I wish I could. Dad and I will be back tomorrow.
Just get some rest until then.
just feels like there is more liquid building in my throat
she said shes suffering from the same thing
Must be a bug going around.
It’s not babe. Trust me. That stuff isn’t real.
Stop. You’re going to be fine.
Sit and breath in deep. In and out. Inhale, exhale.
feel like i need to puke
Make sure and get to the toilet.
the stuff came out of my throat
my stomach doesnt hurt anymore and my headache has gone away
What? What’s going on? Are you still feeling ok?
i dont understand. the stuff that came out of my throat is like…morphing
Ha. Now this is just funny.
Was this whole sick thing a joke??
Ohhhh, and the curse thing. Nice touch.
Sure, sure. What’s happening now? Haha
im in my bedroom with the door locked
Scary. I gotta show your father this. He’ll get a good laugh.
MOM! im serious. It started in my throat then grew
it was bigger then i am, i ran to my room
A mucus ball grew bigger then you?? That’s funny. You have got quite the imagination.
